This is how to how_many_times of string and substring:
  When substring's length is 0, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that limit is diff of string's length and substring's length
  When limit is more than 0, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  Do this sum of limit and 1 times:
    Remember that i is diff of sum of limit and 1 and count
    Remember that piece is ""
    Do this substring's length times:
      Remember that j is diff of substring's length and piece's length
      Remember that piece is "{piece}{item diff of sum of i and j and 1 in string}"
    End do
    When piece is substring, then:
      Increase count
    End when
  End do
  The answer is count
